{"title":"NIS2334复习","uid":"e1111deafa6114c30ea11c8e9b534620","slug":"ICE2501_Review","date":"2024-06-02T14:16:00.000Z","updated":"2024-06-20T08:41:25.562Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ICE2501_Review.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"零碎知识点\">零碎知识点</h1>\r\n<h2 id=\"signals-and-systems\">signals and systems</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"sa函数\">Sa函数</h3>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192131837.png\" alt=\"image-20240619212951523\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192131635.png\" alt=\"image-20240619213005585\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"basic-signals\">basic signals</h3>\r\n<p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192052116.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240619205254096\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192131631.png\" alt=\"image-20240619205823180\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192242716.png\" alt=\"image-20240619224229698\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192131156.png\" alt=\"image-20240619213141127\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192131102.png\" alt=\"image-20240619213157072\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"unit-impulseunit-step\">unit impulse/unit step</h3>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192132391.png\" alt=\"image-20240619213203366\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192132969.png\" alt=\"image-20240619213211942\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192132752.png\" alt=\"image-20240619213242719\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192214757.png\" alt=\"image-20240619221409739\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192216060.png\" alt=\"image-20240619221633043\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192216848.png\" alt=\"image-20240619221642830\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"properties\">properties</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>time shift</li>\r\n<li>time reversal</li>\r\n<li>time scaling</li>\r\n<li><strong>combination transformation</strong></li>\r\n<li>differentiate</li>\r\n<li>integar</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"else\">else</h3>\r\n<p><strong>odd signals and even signals</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192256185.png\" alt=\"image-20240619225641165\" style=\"zoom: 50%;\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>real and imaginary part</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192300370.png\" alt=\"image-20240619230053344\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></p>\r\n<h2 id=\"fs\">FS</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"dtfs\">DTFS</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>傅里叶级数是对信号在能量上的最佳近似</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"group-delay\">group delay</h2>\r\n<p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406201508152.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620150855122\" /></p>\r\n<h1 id=\"可能试题\">可能试题</h1>\r\n<h2 id=\"signals-and-systems-1\">signals and systems</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"judge-period\">Judge period</h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"ct\">CT</h4>\r\n<p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192047031.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240619204658938\" /></p>\r\n<h4 id=\"dt\">DT</h4>\r\n<p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192218783.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240619221849763\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192247138.png\" alt=\"image-20240619224736112\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"energy-and-power\">energy and power</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192048212.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240619204817186\" /></p></li>\r\n<li><p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192055027.png\"\r\nalt=\"111\" /></p></li>\r\n<li><p>(finite) Power signal：with infinite energy</p></li>\r\n<li><p>(finite) Energy signal：with zero average power</p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192049554.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240619204940536\" /></p>\r\n<details>\r\n<summary>\r\n例题\r\n</summary>\r\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406201039789.png\" alt=\"image-20240620103956762\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" />\r\n</details>\r\n<h3 id=\"combination-transformation\">combination transformation</h3>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192251930.png\" alt=\"image-20240619225141906\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"system-properties\">system properties</h3>\r\n<p><strong>causality</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>stability</strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192305733.png\" alt=\"image-20240619230532712\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>time\r\ninvariance</strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192312812.png\" alt=\"image-20240619231227795\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>linearity</strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192306484.png\" alt=\"image-20240619230608465\" style=\"zoom: 80%;\" />\r\n--- how to prove</p>\r\n<p><a\r\nhref=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ac411h7am/?vd_source=5770856d2f35c8b47bf20bc120936faf\">十分钟搞定时变系统的判断_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>变系数则为时变</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"lti\">LTI</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"convolution\">convolution</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>impulse response/shift impulse response</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>公式</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192325661.png\" alt=\"image-20240619232549126\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"C:/Users/Windows11/AppData/Roaming/Typora/typora-user-images/image-20240619234302902.png\" alt=\"image-20240619234302902\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>冲激卷积</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192328045.png\" alt=\"image-20240619232759338\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192348180.png\" alt=\"image-20240619234812154\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>方法</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>图解法：<a\r\nhref=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV11U4y1m7bC/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click&amp;vd_source=5770856d2f35c8b47bf20bc120936faf\">【第37题】▏知识点：图解法计算卷积积分_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></p></li>\r\n<li><p>解析法</p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>速成</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192337809.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240619233704791\" /></li>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192337646.png\" alt=\"image-20240619233735628\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /></li>\r\n<li>利用冲激函数</li>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192340809.png\" alt=\"image-20240619234021791\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /></li>\r\n<li>直接替换其中内容</li>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192341922.png\" alt=\"image-20240619234124902\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math inline\">\\(n_1 + n_2\\)</span></li>\r\n<li>分配律/交换律/结合律</li>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192349510.png\" alt=\"image-20240619234956483\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></li>\r\n<li>scaling性质：左边成一个右边乘两个<span\r\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{1}{a}\\)</span></li>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192355647.png\" alt=\"image-20240619235510621\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /></li>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200001211.png\" alt=\"image-20240620000132188\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>常见卷积</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>门函数的卷积\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406192359142.png\" alt=\"image-20240619235912121\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></li>\r\n<li>单位<strong>跃阶</strong>响应</li>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200031843.png\" alt=\"image-20240620003115822\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></li>\r\n<li><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200031643.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620003142623\" />difference 和defferential</li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>系统性质</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>casality:看<span class=\"math inline\">\\(h(t)&lt;0\\)</span>的部分</li>\r\n<li>stability:<img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200030537.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620003013516\" />绝对可积</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"linear-functions\"><span style=\"color:#CC0000;\">linear\r\nfunctions</span></h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"differential\">differential</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>zero input/zs</li>\r\n<li>free/force</li>\r\n<li>齐次解/特解</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>方法</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>经典解法\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>特解：<img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200041023.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620004151002\" /></li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n<li>系统解法</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><a\r\nhref=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Xv4y1o7f9/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click&amp;vd_source=5770856d2f35c8b47bf20bc120936faf\">经典解法与系统解法_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></p>\r\n<h4 id=\"difference\">difference</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>将y化为方程</li>\r\n<li><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200052543.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620005247519\" /></li>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200104579.png\" alt=\"image-20240620010407557\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /></li>\r\n<li>神奇的递归法</li>\r\n<li><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200103701.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620010257764\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<details>\r\n<summary>\r\n例题\r\n</summary>\r\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200115892.png\" alt=\"image-20240620011454915\" />\r\n</details>\r\n<h2 id=\"fourier-series\">Fourier Series</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"ctfs\"><span style=\"color:#CC0000;\">CTFS</span></h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"形式\">形式</h4>\r\n<p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200121418.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620012125396\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>复指数形式</strong></p>\r\n<p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200129431.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620012930413\" /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_n\\)</span>共轭对称</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>三角形式</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200130099.png\" alt=\"image-20240620013012074\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>余弦形式</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200133498.png\" alt=\"image-20240620013349474\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200138491.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620013832469\" /></p></li>\r\n<li><p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200139264.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620013907241\" /></p></li>\r\n<li><h4 id=\"性质\">性质</h4></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"dtfs-1\">DTFS</h3>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406201047962.png\" alt=\"image-20240620104702934\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"convergence\">convergence</h3>\r\n<p><strong>充分</strong></p>\r\n<p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200142342.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620014212323\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Dirichlet conditions</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>finite maxima and minima</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img\r\nsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200141711.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20240620014128685\" /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200143610.png\" alt=\"image-20240620014327590\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"paswell-energy\">paswell-energy</h3>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sensuschung/wordpress_image/master/blog/202406200120611.png\" alt=\"image-20240620012022581\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 id=\